      "text": [
        " : فِي اَلرَّجُلِ يَمُوتُ مُرْتَدّاً عَنِ اَلْإِسْلاَمِ وَ لَهُ أَوْلاَدٌ وَ مَالٌ قَالَ \"مَالُهُ لِوُلْدِهِ اَلْمُسْلِمِينَ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3555 - Ibn Faddal reported from Aban that Abu Abdullah (as) said:\n\"If a man dies as an apostate from Islam and he has children and wealth, his wealth is to be inherited by his Muslim children.\""
        ]
      }
